          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Affordable Solar Energy for Our Communities Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Energy to establish a program to provide financial assistance, such as grants or low-interest loans, to certain entities for the planning or installation of solar facilities that benefit certain low-income households.</p>]]>
